collections.name: Onyx Void
collections.description:
Onyx Void is a mysterious enforcer from the neon-lit underbelly of a cyberpunk metropolis. Once human, his body was enhanced with experimental biotech, leaving his face a permanent skull-like mask with glowing red eyes—a haunting reminder of the price he paid for power.

Draped in bold streetwear fused with high-tech elements, he blends seamlessly into the underground world of rogue hackers, mercenaries, and crime syndicates. His gold chains symbolize his past wealth, while his baggy, layered clothing hides an array of concealed gadgets and weapons.

With unmatched agility and brutal efficiency, Onyx Void is both feared and respected. He rarely speaks, but when he does, his words carry the weight of someone who has seen too much. His motive remains a mystery—is he hunting revenge, freedom, or something far more sinister?

collections.name: TORIBIO
collections.description: Toribio is a kind, friendly, yet shy and reserved teenager. He stands out because he prefers solitude, finding comfort in it while hiding his feelings to avoid being hurt. Struggling to fit into a world focused on appearances, he often feels out of place. Despite his warmth, he keeps his emotions hidden, fearing rejection and disappointment. He longs to belong, but is unsure how to navigate social expectations while staying true to himself. Yet, he is a fighter, constantly demonstrating his bravery and intelligence to break through to the world and make himself known.
